jo sachche premi hain kisi se dar nahin sakate
jo pyaar karate hain vo kabhi mar nahin sakate
ham pyaar karane vaale har baar kasam lenge
ji ji ke marenge ham mar mar ke janam lenge
jo sachche premi hainhamein saath jina hamein saath marana
nahin dar kuda ka duniya se kya hai darana
pyaar hi hai kuda pyaar imaan hai
pyaar se premiyon ki pahachaan hai
is pahachaan ki rusavaayi premi kar nahin sakate
jo pyaar karate hainpremi jang pyaar vaali haar nahin sakate
log sachche aashiqon ko kabhi maar nahin sakate
pyaar ki lau na dushman bujha paayenge
naam chaahat ka vo na mita paayenge
kat jaate hain aashiq jhuka vo sar nahin sakate
jo pyaar karate hainhamaare pyaar ke dushman agar nazadik aayenge
hamaare pyaar ki chingaariyon se jal jaayenge
muhabbat mit nahin sakati kabhi duniya ki nafarat se
kuda ka naam chalata hai to ik naam-e-mohabbat se